<rss xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Linksphotograph 的 bilibili 空间</title><link>https://space.bilibili.com/3816626</link><ns0:link href="http://blazing-dolphin.pikapod.net/bilibili/user/video/3816626" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" /><description>Linksphotograph 的 bilibili 空间 - Powered by RSSHub</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>contact@rsshub.app (RSSHub)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/face/2827281d7fd11cd62d9cc355039860cd2979970b.jpg</url><title>Linksphotograph 的 bilibili 空间</title><link>https://space.bilibili.com/3816626</link></image><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Dec 2025 01:03:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>5</ttl><item><title>和李现，徒步在西藏库拉岗日</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115684776345914&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1jy2CBNEDL" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/0263aa1fd7e1befd1c116de98bf68b7d8adeca9c.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; -</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1jy2CBNEDL</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1jy2CBNEDL</guid><pubDate>Wed, 10 Dec 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>中国顶级山水？桂林阳朔的终极打开方式</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115609614420658&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1qmUUBsERW" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/b686c491a6fc454a7230335e079554986e4146e8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 去年第一次来到阳朔的时候就被这里的喀斯特地貌惊艳，心想一定要再回到这里，拍下属于这里的故事。拍摄设备 ：Nikon Zr</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qmUUBsERW</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qmUUBsERW</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Nov 2025 04:00:34 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>Links｜终于来到“世界中心”！徒步52公里，我找到了冈仁波齐转山的意义</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115552219565250&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1YyCCBWEa3" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/1df17bdbd3e5faf7799476f54c23a79d5a664c6b.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 每一年，都会有来自世界各地的信徒来到西藏，踏上冈仁波齐的转山之路。所谓“转山”，指的是沿着圣山的外转线徒步一周，全程约48公里，平均海拔高达5000米，是一次对身体与心灵的双重考验。 而这一次，我带着 OPPO Find X9 Pro 出发，踏上了属于自己的转山旅程。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1YyCCBWEa3</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1YyCCBWEa3</guid><pubDate>Sat, 15 Nov 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>用iPhone17Pro能拍出怎么样的影像？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115219409928246&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1LhptzLEWA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/37b374b5a9a89d0774cc2a84119ee824463e1427.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; </description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LhptzLEWA</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LhptzLEWA</guid><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 12:40:26 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>天呐 两个Tim！我们采访了苹果CEO</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115195502396954&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1y5pEzNEd7" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/5e114551272bd47ffc473110cffd32459181db0c.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 感谢apple团队，感谢影视飓风，感谢Tim，这一次，我们采访到了苹果CEO，库克先生。 制作@影视飓风</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1y5pEzNEd7</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1y5pEzNEd7</guid><pubDate>Sat, 13 Sep 2025 08:15:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>我是第一个上岛的中国人？在世界上最孤独的房子里过一夜！</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115140875780375&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1uparzhEjs" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/4b40a4c3f58eccddc10a892ba823b35304eb7d9a.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 等待三年后，我们终于得到了一个机会，去世界上最孤独的房子里过夜一晚。特别鸣谢@巡天者叶梓颐 、Halldor Kvaran、Aki。感谢安克能量舱对本期节目的大力支持，165W Max多口快充，25000mAh超大容量，超级适合外出旅行。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1uparzhEjs</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1uparzhEjs</guid><pubDate>Thu, 04 Sep 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>只有0.01%的人才能做到！攀岩登山意大利多洛米蒂三峰山</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115101348660921&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1zgeUzzEU9" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/585da29b60b2aafe1d94f24936ec1fa5ca8e72ad.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 奇妙的是，三年前我在山脚下拍了一张照片，拍到了夜攀三峰山的人发出的手电亮光，三年后，我成为了那个人！📷 Insta360 AcePro 2 、Go3S、 X5全景相机</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1zgeUzzEU9</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1zgeUzzEU9</guid><pubDate>Thu, 28 Aug 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>带着32万的相机去旅行，我拍到了...</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115060596804195&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1JkegzPEWz" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/4e7543964eb57eecbc93933817ce8340c856a424.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 久违的单人摄影之旅 哈苏H6D-400MS</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1JkegzPEWz</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1JkegzPEWz</guid><pubDate>Thu, 21 Aug 2025 04:10:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>有一天，太阳没有落下</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115021304561914&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1LsbhzBEfJ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/352198171bd65ae5adc9e32c4540a1202963a424.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 时隔三个月，我们又回到了格陵兰岛。和凛冽的寒冬不同，夏天的格陵兰有着永不落下的太阳，无论什么时候抬头看，太阳都高高的挂在那里。就好像小时候幻想的那样，只要我不睡着，这一天就永远不会结束... 而这一次我们居然还走进了因纽特人的家里，吃到了鲸鱼肉....</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LsbhzBEfJ</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LsbhzBEfJ</guid><pubDate>Thu, 14 Aug 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>Links｜葡萄牙最高峰，原来藏在大西洋中央</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114981760732685&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV17WtPzhE4m" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/7881b5d48646b605e7b2db2061f3d82d63dfd502.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 和螃蟹双人成行，抵达葡萄牙最高峰！ 这一次，我们登顶了葡萄牙的最高峰Pico 山(Montanha do Pico). 它位于亚速尔群岛的Pico岛，地处北大西洋，接近欧亚板块与北美板块的交界地带，也是葡萄牙境内最高点。 海拔 2,351米Pico 是一座休眠火山，最后一次喷发是在 1718年，它从海平面拔地而起，是名副其实的“海中之山”。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV17WtPzhE4m</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV17WtPzhE4m</guid><pubDate>Thu, 07 Aug 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>links｜大西洋上只有300人的孤岛，却藏着地球最震撼的火山奇观</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114942367762120&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV19u8BzREBk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/2111111acb4d251f900bf5c852556005938add4b.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 使用相机： LUMIX S1RM2 LUMIX S 24-60mm F2.8 LUMIX S 18mm F1.8</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV19u8BzREBk</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV19u8BzREBk</guid><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>挑战在北极因纽特人的冰屋里过一夜！格陵兰岛冰屋体验｜ 4K杜比视界</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114648732927287&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1vaT9z1E4S" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/59ed7fed9ab142565891e9bf82a251bf132c7bd7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 在生命难以存活的北极，我们住进了因纽特人的冰屋！使用相机：Sony A1M2&amp;amp; A7S3 FE16mm F1.8G FE 28-70mm F2 GM</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vaT9z1E4S</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vaT9z1E4S</guid><pubDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>Links｜隐藏着600万年的地球记忆！探索日本最神秘的离岛群--隐岐诸岛 ｜SONY FX2</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114585180835480&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1ydjizBE1o" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/d51fa9bcf801d45bd5f092ece3228a8ba20a0745.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 我们生活在同一片大陆上，但却不共享时间，有人生活在现代城市里，有人生活在被时间遗忘的小岛上，而这座岛屿，隐藏着地球的记忆。 &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;这次我拿着最新发布的Sony FX2，第一次用电影机，和大家一起探索，隐岐诸岛的秘密。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ydjizBE1o</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ydjizBE1o</guid><pubDate>Thu, 29 May 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>和极速拍档一起登雪山,会发生什么样的故事？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114534513641656&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1syE9zoEGA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/e668f6cbb3383e178a6c7aaad672563e667fcd8a.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; </description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1syE9zoEGA</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1syE9zoEGA</guid><pubDate>Wed, 21 May 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>【Links】飞跃13000公里，我们抵达了北极的心脏！格陵兰乌玛那刻｜4K杜比视界</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114501227645137&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1fwEwzeEPp" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/aa709567ee55a7261b96117e4290d8bacd4c1448.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 在格陵兰有一个传说，每一个造访乌玛纳克（Uummannaq）的人，都会把一部分心灵留在这片土地，在之后的日子，它将不断召唤你回去。拍摄器材：DJI Mavic4 Pro</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fwEwzeEPp</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fwEwzeEPp</guid><pubDate>Wed, 14 May 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>【Links】用相机定格时间！我留住了春天！富士GFX100RF</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114447926431654&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1T6VFzAEkL" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/3f133db863427a650debcbe3b1676cf6975c2236.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; </description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1T6VFzAEkL</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1T6VFzAEkL</guid><pubDate>Sun, 04 May 2025 10:01:24 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>我来到了世界上最大的岛屿，北极格陵兰岛！</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114391856971854&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1FqLizZEyo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/b467ee6660b615e8fde02e901d662253aded7a2f.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 这一次我们终于解锁了北极圈的另一片土地：格陵兰岛。这是世界上最大的岛屿，是无比纯洁又神秘的大地，我们在这里，又发生了新的故事！ 感谢科颜氏高保湿霜陪我走过一个又一个极限征程！</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1FqLizZEyo</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1FqLizZEyo</guid><pubDate>Fri, 25 Apr 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>【Links】跑遍全世界，我搜集到的...</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114347514791475&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1GMoMYfESS" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/52021e88924f2d6879d78f943be0166e8ae96c8e.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 这是一天中最神秘的时间，每天太阳在地平线下4度到6度之间的时候，阳光无法直射到地面，透过长长的大气层后，只剩下蓝光散射在整片天空中，整个世界也就被染成了深邃的蓝色。而这种现象通常只会持续30分钟左右，因此它十分珍贵。只会存在于白昼和黑夜交替的短暂空缺里，这是我一天中最喜欢的时刻---- 蓝调时间，而这一次，让我们和CHANEL J12 BLEU腕表，一起追寻蓝调时间。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1GMoMYfESS</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1GMoMYfESS</guid><pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 04:21:24 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>我来到了世界降雪量第一的城市--日本青森</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114159526154035&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1HvQ3YgE4F" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/c31d8fd76b7945353f1a59522494c2da99ffaac1.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 当你们看到这期视频的时候，我已经奔赴下一个冰天雪地中了，期望可以有好运气，可以抓住冬天最后的尾巴📷 SONY A1M2 &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;SONY A7S3&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;SONY FE 28-70mm F2 GM&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;SONY FE 24-70mm F2.8 GM II&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;SONY FE 14mm F1.8 GM*本期胶片部分因为个人喜好，保留了一定的偏色和风格化</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1HvQ3YgE4F</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1HvQ3YgE4F</guid><pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>在美国国家公园，我找到了全世界最大的树｜Links的美西之旅 下集</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114142832754854&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1BPRnYAEx6" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/0db893292e714906cd515bdb0389273b59f78ebe.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 美国旅行下集来啦！这一次，我们去到了拥有世界上体积最大的树的美国杉国家公园，还去到了北美洲最低、最干旱以及最热的地区死亡谷，这里曾经拥有地球上最高气温的观测纪录56.7 °C...</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1BPRnYAEx6</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1BPRnYAEx6</guid><pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>为了追寻苹果壁纸，我站在了地球的大脑上！美西自驾之旅（上集）</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=114105352523264&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1qZ9nYAEqy" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a5fd32752b64c3b45e3220d4dc035da1ea2c79f7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 如果你是一个Mac用户，或者仅仅只是看过它的广告，那也一定会对它的壁纸印象深刻。对我来说，最最吸引我眼球的就是近些年来的Mojave，Sequoia，White Pocket，他们展示了美国西部的沙漠、红衫森林以及高山峡谷的风景，而这也在我心中种下了一颗种子，我想去亲眼看看苹果壁纸里的世界。于是我们就这样跟着理想L9一起，踏上了在美国追寻苹果壁纸的旅程…</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qZ9nYAEqy</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qZ9nYAEqy</guid><pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 10:05:30 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>和Links爬了一趟雪山，我悟了。</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113859029375092&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1fQwme8Eqt" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/bc828f607893cf84b3a15983bd59d4e684835535.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 这次我们前往日本，想带你看看Links是如何创作的，同时我们也想跟随Links一起体验爬雪山的感觉。然而，没想到上了雪山之后，我们竟然面临了生死抉择。如果你喜欢这期节目，请多多支持我们，并把视频发给你的朋友们一起看看！</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fQwme8Eqt</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fQwme8Eqt</guid><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>只存在1天的乌托邦？72小时极限前往日本最北端露营跨年</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113820592833190&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1Aac2eaEYk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/9c58ecc12d03ce19bb07037e3c4e3b3f12d15262.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 很多年前，我看过一部NHK的纪录片，记录了前往北海道最北端跨年的人们的72小时。从那时起，我心中也种下了一颗种子，希望有一天自己也可以去到那里，度过一年中的最后一天，而现在我终于实现了这个愿望！感谢科颜氏高保湿霜对本期节目的大力支持，期待我们可以一起前往北极！</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Aac2eaEYk</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Aac2eaEYk</guid><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 04:26:35 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>全球仅此一家！住进波音747的驾驶舱？盘点我住过的5个奇特住宿地</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113728703957378&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV13HC8YpEY2" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/f2df125f4a21a66a660e72562dab2611966f218e.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 以往我们的旅行经常睡车里或者睡帐篷，而今年，我们住到了一些神奇且有趣的住宿地比如波音747的驾驶舱和免费的太空舱，甚至还有冰块做的酒店…感谢碧欧泉对本期节目的支持，碧欧泉「水动力」保湿乳，集「补水、保湿、修护」于一体，男士冬天精简护肤必备，清冽海洋香宛如海岸迎风的自由气息，水润且澎湃。希望我们新的一年可以和碧欧泉一起澎湃前行！</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV13HC8YpEY2</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV13HC8YpEY2</guid><pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 10:02:15 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>【Links】我登上了瑞士马特洪峰</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113629097689624&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV13qqkYuEGo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/9b1394a1efff961093dda31c235b63e6ab8b2279.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 历时九个月，我终于登山了那座山，实现了两年前的心愿，人真的可以做出一些超越想象的事。这次登山我带的是Insta 360的 X4全景相机，完全解放双手。一路上就像有人跟拍。在阿尔卑斯山地区，我们也看到很多登山者都在使用X4记录登山过程。GO3S轻便又小巧，一直带在我的头盔上，帮我记录攀登第一视角记录。 同时我还带了一台ACE来拍摄B-roll。同时Insta360正在举办征稿活动，期待爱摄影和创作的朋友们带 #影石创作大赛# 在全平台投稿参与。&amp;nbsp;谢谢insta360，谢谢阿楚，俊甫和502，以及谢谢</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV13qqkYuEGo</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV13qqkYuEGo</guid><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:03:06 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>英国！欢迎进入魔法世界｜Links的古堡探险和天空岛车中泊</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113593462817078&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1znimYhEpk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/cff6d7073f7e27cef21c6a5d8922e602b73e6bff.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 勇闯英格兰 上集</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1znimYhEpk</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1znimYhEpk</guid><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>我在英国住到了一间完全免费的海边瞭望站｜苏格兰天空岛的奇遇！Links 4K杜比视界</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113555210896089&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1vzBRYJEmp" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/4bb00284ef12f4ae536048e5454b33d198cf4916.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 林克斯和小螃蟹勇闯英国！下集</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vzBRYJEmp</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1vzBRYJEmp</guid><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>一年仅开放一次！现实中的诺亚方舟？斯瓦尔巴全球种子库｜Links 4K杜比视界</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113278353147125&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1iV2NYaEcF" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/4963f14be1a56e6e11a2c2c3ecec2c3c8a056b0b.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 为了在大规模的区域性或全球性危机出现期间防止某些种子基因的遗失，并进一步保存和备份种子的样本，挪威政府于北冰洋斯瓦巴群岛上建造一座了非营利储藏库，用于保存全世界的农作物种子，这也是全球最大的种子库。斯瓦尔巴全球种子库建于斯瓦尔巴群岛永久冻土区一带的砂岩山内部120米处，建筑物的设计可承受里氏震级10.0的地震，周围也长年覆盖永久冻土，即使岛内的冰帽融化，种子库仍然能保持设备和建筑物的干燥。 由于斯瓦尔巴群岛产煤矿，为种子库制冷机的动力提供原料来源，使其能进一步将种子冷却至摄氏−18℃的最佳温度， 且即</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1iV2NYaEcF</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1iV2NYaEcF</guid><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>我来到了世界上最北的城市，一个永久免签的地方｜Links的北极Vlog 上集</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113216227118937&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1H5xie8EJZ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/91cc3d162dca2ab250dd907c261c1e69321444ab.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 这是上集</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1H5xie8EJZ</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1H5xie8EJZ</guid><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item><item><title>徒步55公里！穿越世界最美徒步路线｜冰岛兰德曼纳劳卡</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=113159553746883&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1b2tEeaE1M" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/ee87667afc4a46e0a1a927e53a9c2f1c425e4754.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 为了弥补第一次去索斯莫克因为下雨只能仓促逃离的遗憾，我们选择在今年，徒步55公里，探索最神秘的内陆高地。 在无人区重装徒步的每一天，都像是在玩一个真人版生存游戏，每一天都在开启地球的新地图。我们成为了真正的！大地探索家，在这段旅程里，我们还遇到了一个快乐的法国小哥...</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1b2tEeaE1M</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1b2tEeaE1M</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><author>Linksphotograph</author></item></channel></rss>